data.description: Great home for sale in Hixson.  This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home offer generous space over two levels.  The main level has a large living area and flex space which could be the dining room, office, kids-zone, etc.  The kitchen has white cabinets and lots of counter space.  There is an island for additional storage and prep area.  Also on this level are three bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Downstairs you'll find another living space with woodburning fireplace, and another flex space that could be used as a 4th bedroom or office, etc.  The half bath and laundry room finish out the lower level.  This home is fenced in both in the backyard and front yard.  And the roof is only 5 years old.  Don't let this one get away.  Call today for your personal showing.
